But our species will dwell
on Earth for about as long

00:37:13.980 --> 00:37:18.660 align:middle line:10%
as our Sun continues to shine,
which, by some estimates,

00:37:18.660 --> 00:37:22.620 align:middle line:10%
is about four
million years more.

00:37:22.620 --> 00:37:25.080 align:middle line:10%
If that's the case,
I asked, why then

00:37:25.080 --> 00:37:28.860 align:middle line:10%
are you so keen on launching
the scientific investigation

00:37:28.860 --> 00:37:31.290 align:middle line:10%
of kundalini now?

00:37:31.290 --> 00:37:35.580 align:middle line:84%
Because, he said, it is the
safest and most effective

00:37:35.580 --> 00:37:39.330 align:middle line:84%
way to rid the world of
the overhanging threat

00:37:39.330 --> 00:37:40.845 align:middle line:90%
of a nuclear war.

00:37:40.845 --> 00:37:43.560 align:middle line:10%
To my way of
thinking, that is what

00:37:43.560 --> 00:37:49.230 align:middle line:10%
distinguishes an illuminated
yogi from an ordinary person.

00:37:49.230 --> 00:37:52.920 align:middle line:10%
He or she becomes a spiritual
genius and a prophet

00:37:52.920 --> 00:37:57.115 align:middle line:10%
able to see into the
future, both near and far.

00:37:57.115 --> 00:38:01.680 align:middle line:10%
And because of the spiritual
genius or illuminated genius

00:38:01.680 --> 00:38:04.410 align:middle line:10%
can see into the future,
such men and women

00:38:04.410 --> 00:38:08.380 align:middle line:10%
are essential for our
survival in the atomic age.

00:38:08.380 --> 00:38:13.650 align:middle line:84%
>> Another part to it is, I
believe he was sure in himself

00:38:13.650 --> 00:38:19.020 align:middle line:84%
that this investigation would
bring out some surprises

00:38:19.020 --> 00:38:22.650 align:middle line:84%
for the scientific community
in terms of what their theories

00:38:22.650 --> 00:38:27.090 align:middle line:84%
are about consciousness, about
the mind, about the brain,

00:38:27.090 --> 00:38:29.470 align:middle line:84%
and about the evolution
of consciousness.

00:38:29.470 --> 00:38:32.340 align:middle line:84%
And that's how science has
advanced usually that there's

00:38:32.340 --> 00:38:34.800 align:middle line:90%
a contradiction somewhere.

00:38:34.800 --> 00:38:37.490 align:middle line:84%
Whatever the theory
is they have,

00:38:37.490 --> 00:38:39.090 align:middle line:84%
they come to a bit
of a roadblock,

00:38:39.090 --> 00:38:40.530 align:middle line:90%
and they can't explain that.

00:38:40.530 --> 00:38:42.420 align:middle line:90%
So he was convinced of that.

00:38:42.420 --> 00:38:46.530 align:middle line:84%
And a good example of that, in
the last 10 or 15 years anyway,

00:38:46.530 --> 00:38:48.990 align:middle line:84%
is the concept of
neuroplasticity,

00:38:48.990 --> 00:38:52.980 align:middle line:84%
where the neurons in the brain
can make different connections

00:38:52.980 --> 00:38:56.850 align:middle line:84%
and can lead to changes
in how the brain functions

00:38:56.850 --> 00:38:58.150 align:middle line:90%
in the individual.

00:38:58.150 --> 00:39:02.415 align:middle line:84%
25 years ago, science believed,
well, the brain, that was it.

00:39:02.415 --> 00:39:05.730 align:middle line:84%
It was fixed for life,
and that's all you got.

00:39:05.730 --> 00:39:10.690 align:middle line:84%
So there's a good example
right there, that's current.

00:39:10.690 --> 00:39:13.980 align:middle line:10%
>> And there hasn't been
a scientific investigation

00:39:13.980 --> 00:39:16.620 align:middle line:10%
into the phenomenon
of kundalini.

00:39:16.620 --> 00:39:19.620 align:middle line:10%
Nor has there been any
meaningful research

00:39:19.620 --> 00:39:21.940 align:middle line:10%
into consciousness.

00:39:21.940 --> 00:39:23.340 align:middle line:10%
Why not?

00:39:23.340 --> 00:39:27.450 align:middle line:10%
Because it is not possible
to understand consciousness

00:39:27.450 --> 00:39:30.780 align:middle line:10%
without first
investigating and coming

00:39:30.780 --> 00:39:35.700 align:middle line:10%
to know something more about
the phenomenon of kundalini.

00:39:35.700 --> 00:39:39.360 align:middle line:84%
At present, we have only Gopi
Krishna's inner explorations

00:39:39.360 --> 00:39:40.870 align:middle line:90%
to go by.

00:39:40.870 --> 00:39:45.750 align:middle line:10%
But his observations cannot
be accepted by science until

00:39:45.750 --> 00:39:49.780 align:middle line:10%
and unless they are
verified by experimentation.

00:39:49.780 --> 00:39:53.500 align:middle line:10%
And for this kind of research
to be taken up by science,

00:39:53.500 --> 00:39:57.740 align:middle line:10%
Gopi Krishna's theories need to
be widely discussed and debated

00:39:57.740 --> 00:39:59.650 align:middle line:10%
first.

00:39:59.650 --> 00:40:02.640 align:middle line:10%
For example, if a certain
practice of meditation

00:40:02.640 --> 00:40:06.060 align:middle line:10%
were to culminate in the
production of an Einstein

00:40:06.060 --> 00:40:11.070 align:middle line:10%
or a Plato right before the
eyes of leading scientists,

00:40:11.070 --> 00:40:15.650 align:middle line:10%
they would readily acknowledge
the efficacy of the discipline.

00:40:15.650 --> 00:40:18.960 align:middle line:10%
And then there would be
thousands of emulators,

00:40:18.960 --> 00:40:21.000 align:middle line:10%
all fired up with
the hope of attaining

00:40:21.000 --> 00:40:27.000 align:middle line:10%
to the same extraordinary
state of cosmic consciousness.

00:40:27.000 --> 00:40:29.580 align:middle line:10%
Then all the
resources of science

00:40:29.580 --> 00:40:32.820 align:middle line:10%
would be mobilized to
gain more and more insight

00:40:32.820 --> 00:40:35.140 align:middle line:10%
into this state.

00:40:35.140 --> 00:40:37.630 align:middle line:10%
This concept would put
a different complection

00:40:37.630 --> 00:40:39.780 align:middle line:10%
on religion also.

00:40:39.780 --> 00:40:44.050 align:middle line:10%
It would have to concede that
the whole race is evolving

00:40:44.050 --> 00:40:46.450 align:middle line:10%
in the same direction--

00:40:46.450 --> 00:40:49.525 align:middle line:10%
the direction followed by
the great sages and prophets

00:40:49.525 --> 00:40:51.850 align:middle line:10%
of the past--

00:40:51.850 --> 00:40:55.780 align:middle line:10%
and that it has to
achieve the same goal.

00:40:55.780 --> 00:41:00.655 align:middle line:10%
It also has to be admitted then
that what we call miraculous,

00:41:00.655 --> 00:41:04.600 align:middle line:10%
or supernatural, or
paranormal phenomena

00:41:04.600 --> 00:41:06.850 align:middle line:10%
might be the
outcome of laws that

00:41:06.850 --> 00:41:11.140 align:middle line:10%
rule the spiritual world or
the forces compounding it,

00:41:11.140 --> 00:41:15.070 align:middle line:10%
of which we have no real
awareness at present.

00:41:15.070 --> 00:41:19.030 align:middle line:84%
>> People don't realize
that just as the anatomy

00:41:19.030 --> 00:41:23.200 align:middle line:84%
and physiology of the physical
body is the same no matter what

00:41:23.200 --> 00:41:27.700 align:middle line:84%
your religion, the anatomy
and physiology of the soul is

00:41:27.700 --> 00:41:30.770 align:middle line:84%
the same no matter
what your religion.

00:41:30.770 --> 00:41:32.860 align:middle line:84%
So if you were to
compare, for example,

00:41:32.860 --> 00:41:37.210 align:middle line:84%
Saint Teresa of
Avila's Interior Castle

00:41:37.210 --> 00:41:40.270 align:middle line:84%
and her Christian writings
from the 15th century

00:41:40.270 --> 00:41:43.060 align:middle line:84%
about her kundalini
awakening, if you

00:41:43.060 --> 00:41:45.760 align:middle line:84%
were to put that side by
side with Gopi Krishna's

00:41:45.760 --> 00:41:48.010 align:middle line:84%
description of his
kundalini awakening,

00:41:48.010 --> 00:41:51.320 align:middle line:84%
they are both saying
the same thing.

00:41:51.320 --> 00:41:54.670 align:middle line:84%
And that's what's really
neat, because no matter what

00:41:54.670 --> 00:41:58.220 align:middle line:84%
your religion is, it
is the same thing.

00:41:58.220 --> 00:42:00.910 align:middle line:10%
>> It all came out of
the study of yogis,

00:42:00.910 --> 00:42:06.610 align:middle line:10%
and advanced meditators, and
meditators that had abilities

00:42:06.610 --> 00:42:10.000 align:middle line:10%
and capacities to change
how their body, their mind,

00:42:10.000 --> 00:42:14.290 align:middle line:10%
their brain worked in ways that
conventional Western medicine

00:42:14.290 --> 00:42:16.790 align:middle line:10%
said was impossible.

00:42:16.790 --> 00:42:22.690 align:middle line:84%
And the methods and techniques
that are employed in yoga

00:42:22.690 --> 00:42:26.320 align:middle line:84%
were originally discovered
through the actions

00:42:26.320 --> 00:42:28.570 align:middle line:90%
of awaken kundalini.

00:42:28.570 --> 00:42:31.120 align:middle line:84%
What we think of yoga
postures in the West,

00:42:31.120 --> 00:42:35.590 align:middle line:84%
the Hatha yoga asanas,
they were first observed

00:42:35.590 --> 00:42:37.810 align:middle line:84%
and continue to be
observed in people

00:42:37.810 --> 00:42:39.820 align:middle line:90%
who have awakened kundalini.

00:42:39.820 --> 00:42:42.520 align:middle line:84%
They may go through some
of these postures quite

00:42:42.520 --> 00:42:43.990 align:middle line:90%
spontaneously.

00:42:43.990 --> 00:42:48.130 align:middle line:84%
Well, we're already studying
the Hatha yoga and other things

00:42:48.130 --> 00:42:50.455 align:middle line:84%
related to breathwork
and mindfulness

00:42:50.455 --> 00:42:53.640 align:middle line:84%
that have very good
health benefits

00:42:53.640 --> 00:42:56.620 align:middle line:84%
and that are very important
for all of society in terms

00:42:56.620 --> 00:43:00.520 align:middle line:84%
of changing cardiovascular
health, decreasing stress,

00:43:00.520 --> 00:43:04.670 align:middle line:84%
stress that exacerbates all
kinds of medical conditions.

00:43:04.670 --> 00:43:09.070 align:middle line:84%
So it would be a
very fruitful way

00:43:09.070 --> 00:43:16.030 align:middle line:84%
of being able to pursue what
of the many kundalini-related

00:43:16.030 --> 00:43:19.890 align:middle line:84%
techniques in science from the
ancient sages of the Eastern

00:43:19.890 --> 00:43:25.090 align:middle line:84%
tradition would have
medical benefits today.

00:43:25.090 --> 00:43:31.150 align:middle line:10%
We're in the earliest stages
of infancy of the research.

00:43:31.150 --> 00:43:34.030 align:middle line:10%
Because research
takes money, and money

00:43:34.030 --> 00:43:37.210 align:middle line:10%
goes after legitimate problems.

00:43:37.210 --> 00:43:41.500 align:middle line:84%
There's not enough belief or
understanding about kundalini.

00:43:41.500 --> 00:43:44.050 align:middle line:84%
So I think there's a lot
of intermediary steps

00:43:44.050 --> 00:43:45.580 align:middle line:90%
that are being built.

00:43:45.580 --> 00:43:48.910 align:middle line:84%
Because there is money
that's getting funded,

00:43:48.910 --> 00:43:51.490 align:middle line:90%
research being funded--

00:43:51.490 --> 00:43:54.910 align:middle line:84%
for instance,
mindfulness-based relaxation,

00:43:54.910 --> 00:43:58.345 align:middle line:84%
kinds of stress management
exercises, meditation.

00:43:58.345 --> 00:44:00.240 align:middle line:84%
There is meditation
research being done.

00:44:00.240 --> 00:44:04.300 align:middle line:84%
There's certain forms of yoga
starting to be researched.

00:44:04.300 --> 00:44:09.910 align:middle line:84%
The crunch in health dollars
makes it very important

00:44:09.910 --> 00:44:13.510 align:middle line:84%
that we discover ways
to support wellness.

00:44:13.510 --> 00:44:17.920 align:middle line:84%
It's much more cost effective
to support a person's wellness

00:44:17.920 --> 00:44:21.440 align:middle line:84%
than to try and treat
a chronic condition.

00:44:21.440 --> 00:44:25.630 align:middle line:84%
So it's going to be more
effective to try and do

00:44:25.630 --> 00:44:30.640 align:middle line:84%
research and show that
a yoga lifestyle is

00:44:30.640 --> 00:44:32.350 align:middle line:90%
going to be healthier.

00:44:32.350 --> 00:44:34.800 align:middle line:84%
When you look at a country,
for instance, China,

00:44:34.800 --> 00:44:39.040 align:middle line:84%
that has such a huge
population, and yet, you'll

00:44:39.040 --> 00:44:43.720 align:middle line:84%
see in every city,
people doing things

00:44:43.720 --> 00:44:45.610 align:middle line:90%
like Tai Chi in the morning--

00:44:45.610 --> 00:44:48.680 align:middle line:84%
hundreds and hundreds of
people, thousands of people,

00:44:48.680 --> 00:44:51.110 align:middle line:84%
millions of people
across the country.

00:44:51.110 --> 00:44:53.170 align:middle line:90%
And that's been promoted.

00:44:53.170 --> 00:44:55.370 align:middle line:84%
We need to have that
kind of philosophy.

00:44:55.370 --> 00:44:58.690 align:middle line:84%
We need to have in
the West the idea

00:44:58.690 --> 00:45:01.480 align:middle line:84%
of what do we do to
promote optimal health,

00:45:01.480 --> 00:45:03.400 align:middle line:90%
optimal well-being.

00:45:03.400 --> 00:45:07.330 align:middle line:84%
And yoga kinds of practices
can really support that.

00:45:07.330 --> 00:45:11.050 align:middle line:84%
They have a tremendous
amount to give in that way.

00:45:11.050 --> 00:45:14.560 align:middle line:84%
That will be building
bridges towards then

00:45:14.560 --> 00:45:17.560 align:middle line:84%
being able to do research
on sort of the more

00:45:17.560 --> 00:45:23.060 align:middle line:84%
esoteric levels of yoga, things
related to kundalini and energy

00:45:23.060 --> 00:45:23.860 align:middle line:90%
in that.

00:45:23.860 --> 00:45:28.450 align:middle line:10%
>> People will follow
society's rules not out of fear

00:45:28.450 --> 00:45:33.030 align:middle line:10%
of consequences and legalism,
but out of love for mankind.

00:45:33.030 --> 00:45:36.950 align:middle line:84%
Same rules, not
one dot is removed,

00:45:36.950 --> 00:45:41.020 align:middle line:90%
but you follow them out of love.

00:45:41.020 --> 00:45:46.390 align:middle line:84%
And the reason is because
as consciousness grows--

00:45:46.390 --> 00:45:49.300 align:middle line:84%
if you were to be able to
see an individual soul,

00:45:49.300 --> 00:45:51.310 align:middle line:90%
an individual soul is about--

00:45:51.310 --> 00:45:54.400 align:middle line:90%
the average, some are greater--

00:45:54.400 --> 00:45:57.520 align:middle line:84%
the average is about 15 feet
out from the physical body

00:45:57.520 --> 00:45:59.242 align:middle line:90%
or about 30 feet in diameter.

00:45:59.242 --> 00:46:00.200 align:middle line:90%
That's at its smallest.

00:46:00.200 --> 00:46:03.110 align:middle line:90%


00:46:03.110 --> 00:46:07.670 align:middle line:84%
As consciousness
raises, it expands,

00:46:07.670 --> 00:46:09.720 align:middle line:90%
and it gets greater and greater.

00:46:09.720 --> 00:46:12.290 align:middle line:84%
So you have all these people
whose consciousness is focused

00:46:12.290 --> 00:46:14.690 align:middle line:90%
down here, at the lower level.

00:46:14.690 --> 00:46:17.390 align:middle line:84%
Think of a V, and their
consciousness is at the bottom.

00:46:17.390 --> 00:46:20.090 align:middle line:84%
They view everyone else
as separate from them,

00:46:20.090 --> 00:46:22.160 align:middle line:90%
and life is a competition.

00:46:22.160 --> 00:46:24.350 align:middle line:84%
But as your
consciousness raises up,

00:46:24.350 --> 00:46:27.200 align:middle line:84%
you start to realize
these Vs overlap.

00:46:27.200 --> 00:46:30.020 align:middle line:84%
And you start to realize
that that other person's

00:46:30.020 --> 00:46:33.320 align:middle line:90%
consciousness is within yours.

00:46:33.320 --> 00:46:37.160 align:middle line:84%
So you start to
develop some altruism.

00:46:37.160 --> 00:46:42.140 align:middle line:84%
And as you get to a higher
level of consciousness,

00:46:42.140 --> 00:46:46.760 align:middle line:84%
you realize that
everyone exists within

00:46:46.760 --> 00:46:49.310 align:middle line:90%
the same unified consciousness.

00:46:49.310 --> 00:46:52.610 align:middle line:84%
So if I cause harm to you,
I'm causing harm to myself.

00:46:52.610 --> 00:46:55.115 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, I would expect that
there's going to be more

00:46:55.115 --> 00:47:00.710 align:middle line:84%
of individuals being seen as
having these kinds of symptoms

00:47:00.710 --> 00:47:07.640 align:middle line:84%
looking beyond the
psychopathology that is often

00:47:07.640 --> 00:47:11.270 align:middle line:84%
these things are characterized
as and looking for some help

00:47:11.270 --> 00:47:14.870 align:middle line:84%
and saying, wait a minute, this
has to do with transcendent

00:47:14.870 --> 00:47:17.150 align:middle line:90%
states.

00:47:17.150 --> 00:47:20.270 align:middle line:84%
We need to have the kind
of psychology-- and we do,

00:47:20.270 --> 00:47:23.210 align:middle line:84%
in terms of like
transpersonal psychology--

00:47:23.210 --> 00:47:26.840 align:middle line:84%
that says, these kinds of
states aren't pathological,

00:47:26.840 --> 00:47:28.640 align:middle line:90%
these are enlightened states.

00:47:28.640 --> 00:47:31.820 align:middle line:84%
These are optimal states,
these are transcendent states.

00:47:31.820 --> 00:47:34.910 align:middle line:84%
People need to learn how to
integrate those so that they

00:47:34.910 --> 00:47:38.180 align:middle line:90%
don't become dysfunctional.

00:47:38.180 --> 00:47:42.350 align:middle line:84%
But it's a sign that
that's a possibility.

00:47:42.350 --> 00:47:49.670 align:middle line:84%
And how do we develop the kinds
of treatment paradigms, places

00:47:49.670 --> 00:47:53.250 align:middle line:84%
that help people integrate
these experiences?

00:47:53.250 --> 00:47:57.130 align:middle line:84%
>> The thing to be
aware of, though,

00:47:57.130 --> 00:48:00.260 align:middle line:84%
is that in this
process right here,

00:48:00.260 --> 00:48:07.640 align:middle line:84%
where this person could go back
here, there is a process that,

00:48:07.640 --> 00:48:10.580 align:middle line:84%
for a person going through it,
it's very difficult for them

00:48:10.580 --> 00:48:12.940 align:middle line:90%
to identify it.

00:48:12.940 --> 00:48:15.380 align:middle line:84%
And it's what I call the
false kundalini process

00:48:15.380 --> 00:48:18.800 align:middle line:90%
or the false born-again.

00:48:18.800 --> 00:48:22.820 align:middle line:84%
It's a fairly easy process,
if I were ruthless and wanted

00:48:22.820 --> 00:48:27.680 align:middle line:84%
to control people, to
lead them through it.

00:48:27.680 --> 00:48:30.530 align:middle line:84%
What it is, it's a
mind control technique.

00:48:30.530 --> 00:48:32.190 align:middle line:90%
It's really simple.

00:48:32.190 --> 00:48:37.760 align:middle line:84%
It's done quite often in
charismatic churches, where

00:48:37.760 --> 00:48:39.620 align:middle line:84%
you step one, allow the
volume of your voice

00:48:39.620 --> 00:48:44.330 align:middle line:84%
to go up and down; step two,
tell a sad story, happy story,

00:48:44.330 --> 00:48:46.940 align:middle line:84%
knock a person's emotional
consciousness off balance;

00:48:46.940 --> 00:48:52.250 align:middle line:84%
step three, induce guilt,
fear, anger; step 4,

00:48:52.250 --> 00:48:54.500 align:middle line:84%
offer them a way
to get rid of that.

00:48:54.500 --> 00:48:57.660 align:middle line:84%
They will swear on a
Bible they are born-again.

00:48:57.660 --> 00:49:00.140 align:middle line:84%
It has absolutely nothing
to do with religion.

00:49:00.140 --> 00:49:02.420 align:middle line:90%
It is a mind control game.

00:49:02.420 --> 00:49:06.440 align:middle line:84%
It's actually a stage
hypnosis induction technique.

00:49:06.440 --> 00:49:11.780 align:middle line:84%
This also applies to
the kundalini process.

00:49:11.780 --> 00:49:13.610 align:middle line:90%
It's totally false.

00:49:13.610 --> 00:49:18.160 align:middle line:84%
And where it is
so dangerous is--

00:49:18.160 --> 00:49:21.400 align:middle line:84%
the pitfall is that
instead of you surrendering

00:49:21.400 --> 00:49:26.710 align:middle line:84%
to the divine, which is what
takes a person up this slope,

00:49:26.710 --> 00:49:30.370 align:middle line:84%
this person surrenders their
authority to another human

00:49:30.370 --> 00:49:32.980 align:middle line:90%
being.

00:49:32.980 --> 00:49:36.400 align:middle line:84%
This is true on an individual
basis on the spiritual path.

00:49:36.400 --> 00:49:41.060 align:middle line:84%
It's also true on a
greater basis in society.

00:49:41.060 --> 00:49:43.000 align:middle line:84%
For example, the
Germans, the Prussians

00:49:43.000 --> 00:49:47.890 align:middle line:84%
